{"tid":2415439,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女兒抱孫打氣 黎智英露笑容","createTime":"2021-02-20T08:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T08:54:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"790a89a8f378649ee7e445b794b1a18ba7c7658b","tid":2415439,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/XXJSSH2B7FD33OYRKOHAY72KVQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FXXJSSH2B7FD33OYRKOHAY72KVQ%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkhOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=9f16c2a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FXXJSSH2B7FD33OYRKOHAY72KVQ%2F&h=ad34a2f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/XXJSSH2B7FD33OYRKOHAY72KVQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n女兒抱孫打氣 黎智英露笑容<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FWZi-K-Noqfel8QzDLkoadqkAQw=/1724x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5PZCT2VSUVCXDN3LT3HFVUAMLI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFWZi-K-Noqfel8QzDLkoadqkAQw%3D%2F1724x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5PZCT2VSUVCXDN3LT3HFVUAMLI.jpg&h=37ad8ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英昨上庭聆訊後繼續還柙。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】被告壹傳媒創辦人黎智英另因國安法案件而還柙，前日申請保釋失敗，昨繼續由囚車押解上庭。不同親友每天旁聽支持，黎的女兒昨帶來稀客&mdash;&mdash;黎的年幼外孫，抱到被告欄前與黎隔着玻璃短敍。黎面露笑容，在嚴肅的聆訊時間外舒懷片刻。不過，外孫兒在證人作供時間歇發出聲音，最終法官請黎的女兒帶他移步庭外旁聽，以免騷擾審訊。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：事前評估集會和平 稱警執勤容忍  8.18指揮官「維園人潮每小時3萬」<br />\n<br />\n黎智英前日到高等法院，為其勾結外國勢力案件重新申請保釋，因而缺席本案審訊。黎昨「回歸」西九龍法院，被懲教人員帶入被告欄一角後，如常與相熟的其他被告打招呼，亦向旁聽席上的支持者舉手致意。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。"}]}